02:17:24.200 --> 02:17:35.479
God's a covenant-keeping God. God is a blessing God. God wants you to walk in abundance; he doesn't want you to walk in poverty.

02:17:35.480 --> 02:17:49.371
Look, he wants to establish his covenant with you. So, is it about naming and claiming it, blabbing and grabbing it, and all the things people mock all the time?

02:17:49.372 --> 02:17:55.882
Life and death is in the power of your tongue. If you're always talking poverty, out of the abundance of the heart the mouth speaks, you're going to walk in poverty.

02:17:55.883 --> 02:17:59.275
But I'm going to say it out of my mouth: I have creative ideas to get wealth.

02:17:59.276 --> 02:18:05.678
He's going to tell me how to do it. Why? Because he's going to establish his covenant with Brandon Biggs.

02:18:05.679 --> 02:18:10.199
So don't hate me whenever you see my harvest because it's coming.

02:18:10.200 --> 02:18:22.678
I know the cryptos that I've invested in and the one the Lord's told me is going to make me a billionaire. Don't hate me. I'm telling you it's coming.

02:18:22.679 --> 02:18:44.496
'The blessing of the Lord maketh rich and adds no sorrow with it.'Proverbs 10:22: 'The blessing of the Lord, it makes rich and adds no sorrow with it.'That means there's blessing without sorrow.

02:18:44.497 --> 02:18:51.839
It means you ain't having a bad day; you're full of joy. Why? He said good days are coming for the body of Christ.

02:18:51.840 --> 02:19:03.039
Days of fun have just begun. Either you believe it or you don't.

02:19:03.040 --> 02:19:15.959
Why is it so easy to rebuttal that? People get so mad. But he wants you to believe him for more.

02:19:15.960 --> 02:19:21.839
The wealth of the sinner is laid up for the righteous. Why not?

02:19:21.840 --> 02:19:29.558
Satan comes and tries to offer you everything under the sun and say, 'Listen, this is what I'm going to do; you do this for me.'But God said it's all mine.

02:19:29.559 --> 02:19:43.239
And the devil's a copycat. So he wants to copy and do what God will do for the righteous if you're dead to self and he can trust you with it. It's when you're righteous.

02:19:43.240 --> 02:19:51.475
'The blessing of the Lord maketh rich and adds no sorrow with it.'So if you're in right standing with God, he doesn't have a problem with it.

02:19:51.476 --> 02:20:04.479
It's whenever you are letting things control you. 'Let them shout for joy and be glad that favor my righteous cause.

02:20:04.480 --> 02:20:17.919
Yea, let them say continually, "Let the Lord be magnified, which hath pleasure in the prosperity of his servant."'I'm telling you, you want to make a devil mad.

02:20:17.920 --> 02:20:25.727
That's why he hates the Greens, the people of Hobby Lobby and Mart Green, because I know for a fact they give to ministries and blessing.

02:20:25.728 --> 02:20:35.919
They're the ones that bailed out ORU. I think it was $56 million, and if they hadn't had it, ORU would have been closed.

02:20:35.920 --> 02:20:47.919
But God used a billionaire named Green from Hobby Lobby that spoke to his heart and said, 'Bail out ORU.'ORU is where my wife graduated.

02:20:47.920 --> 02:20:56.593
She got her bachelor's there and has her counseling and everything.

02:20:56.594 --> 02:21:01.599
If he wouldn't have built that up, they would have closed it down.

02:21:01.600 --> 02:21:06.799
Thank God, it's a good godly school. They teach the Word there; they love the Lord.

02:21:06.800 --> 02:21:11.432
