02:21:11.433 --> 02:21:25.599
They said, 'Hey, I can write a check for that.'Imagine being able to give a school $56 million—whatever it was, a lot of money.

02:21:25.600 --> 02:21:36.439
Write a check and say, 'Listen, we don't want you to close it down,'where you're the only God-fearing school around, because other than that, you have to go to a secular school.

02:21:36.440 --> 02:21:50.352
So, let's write a check for that because they would have closed the doors. Thank God for the Greens. Thank God for Mardel.

02:21:50.353 --> 02:22:02.399
Thank God so many people have been blessed going to ORU, and the Mabee Center would be called something else because a secular school would have come in and bought that place and they'd be making it a secular school right now.

02:22:02.400 --> 02:22:11.159
But now the Glory Dome will be the Mabee Center because the Greens stood in and helped buy it.

02:22:11.160 --> 02:22:19.479
Thank God. So, who else wants to be a Green? Who wants to write a $58 million check?

02:22:19.480 --> 02:22:25.685
Do you? Can God trust you with it? Could you choke on it if he told you and you were a billionaire?

02:22:25.686 --> 02:22:33.359
If he told you, 'I want you to write them a check so they don't lose it all,'and you go, 'That's a lot of money.'That's why you don't have it.

02:22:33.360 --> 02:22:48.159
The Greens did it. Thank God for them. I don't know why I'm supposed to say all this stuff tonight.

02:22:48.160 --> 02:23:02.183
Stretch yourself. Praise ye the Lord. Blessed is the man that feareth the Lord, that delighteth greatly in his commandments.

02:23:02.184 --> 02:23:09.369
His seed shall be mighty upon the earth. The generation of the upright shall be blessed.

02:23:09.370 --> 02:23:32.799
Wealth and riches shall be in his house, and his righteousness endureth forever.

02:23:32.800 --> 02:23:40.199
Thank you. That's a good one, Braden. I never had that before.

02:23:40.200 --> 02:23:56.678
As you could see, Father, we just thank you, Lord, for this night of prayer. And we lift up Cuba before you. We lift up our nation.

